The South African National Roads Agency SOC Limited (SANRAL) s Southern Region s Michelle Ah Shene, Marketing and Communications Manager (far left) and Xoliswa Chubana, Community Development Project Manager, drew a big crowd to the road agency s stand at the Business Expo &amp; My City Talk event last week (29 June), held at Father s House Church in Port Elizabeth. Information on SANRAL bursary and scholarship programmes as well as SMME involvement on SANRAL projects were provided to visitors.